WEBVTT

00:00:01.240 --> 00:00:02.510
Evening family. Thank you

00:00:02.520 --> 00:00:04.310
for joining me today.

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:06.510
We're going to pray.

00:00:06.520 --> 00:00:08.910
We have work to do, as everybody can

00:00:08.920 --> 00:00:11.830
see on the news.

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.990
As I've been praying over

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.430
all this today—I made those two videos

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:19.390
for you

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:21.590
yesterday—I

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:23.670
had a dream last night. The Lord

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:25.990
visited me. It was actually

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:29.070
an encounter I've never had

00:00:29.080 --> 00:00:30.270
before,

00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:31.590
but it

00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:33.350
shook me a little bit because it was

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:35.390
instruction and correction

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:37.430
from one of my prayer generals. It

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:39.390
was amazing, and I'm not going to

00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:41.590
get into it until I understand it all,

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:43.550
but

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:45.110
I was visited by somebody and the

00:00:45.120 --> 00:00:46.710
Lord spoke to me in a dream through

00:00:46.720 --> 00:00:48.230
this individual;

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:49.790
it was correction

00:00:49.790 --> 00:00:49.800
regarding

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:51.870
some things. I know that

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:53.510
probably won't make sense to some of you

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:55.070
because

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.230
this is like

00:00:57.240 --> 00:00:59.070
spiritual

00:00:59.080 --> 00:01:02.550
algebra, but I'm

00:01:02.560 --> 00:01:05.150
going to go

00:01:05.160 --> 00:01:07.310
a different direction tonight with some

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:08.710
of the things the Lord has instructed me

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:12.670
to do.

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:36.190
I thought this was

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:37.830
Carmex

00:01:37.840 --> 00:01:40.710
for your lips. I

00:01:40.710 --> 00:01:40.720
sat

00:01:40.720 --> 00:01:42.670
here and thought, 'What kind of

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:44.190
new lip balm is this?'So I'm

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:45.910
putting it on my lips and my

00:01:45.910 --> 00:01:45.920
son

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:49.150
said, 'Dad, that's

00:01:49.150 --> 00:01:49.160
glue.'I

00:01:49.160 --> 00:01:54.790
said, 'Oh, glue stick.

00:01:54.800 --> 00:01:57.710
Duh.'I

00:01:57.720 --> 00:01:59.550
had to wipe my face off real

00:01:59.560 --> 00:02:03.510
quick because it was stinging.

00:02:03.510 --> 00:02:03.520
Regarding

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:05.870
the

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:07.150
encounter, I don't want to talk about

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:08.749
that.

00:02:08.759 --> 00:02:11.750
I'm

00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:13.949
just going to give you some scripture

00:02:13.959 --> 00:02:14.990
that I've been

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:19.110
meditating on:

00:02:19.110 --> 00:02:19.120
Psalm

00:02:19.120 --> 00:02:21.949
29:11.

00:02:21.959 --> 00:02:24.670
'The Lord will give strength unto his

00:02:24.680 --> 00:02:26.990
people;

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:29.070
the Lord will bless his people with

00:02:29.080 --> 00:02:30.710
peace.'Right

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:33.150
now, I believe that scripture

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:35.070
stands really strong

00:02:35.070 --> 00:02:35.080
for

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:37.230
me. The Lord will give his people

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.790
peace

00:02:38.790 --> 00:02:38.800
and

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:42.030
strength.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:45.510
Right now, we need strength

00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:47.390
and peace.

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:49.670
But I know what the Lord is instructing

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:50.710
me because I asked, 'What do you want me to

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:51.870
say

00:02:51.880 --> 00:02:54.070
tonight?'He

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:55.870
said, 'Remind them: don't pray the

00:02:55.880 --> 00:02:58.230
news.'If

00:02:58.240 --> 00:02:59.630
you're praying the news, you're

00:02:59.640 --> 00:03:01.509
behind.

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:04.509
Everything that we have seen

00:03:04.519 --> 00:03:07.070
over the last year and a half

00:03:07.080 --> 00:03:10.190
led up to this point.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:13.270
We've been praying over this

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:15.630
for

00:03:15.630 --> 00:03:15.640
weeks—what

00:03:15.640 --> 00:03:18.430
the Holy Spirit warned us about

00:03:18.430 --> 00:03:18.440
concerning

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:21.509
drones, missile attacks,

00:03:21.509 --> 00:03:21.519
and

00:03:21.519 --> 00:03:23.949
Tel

00:03:23.949 --> 00:03:23.959
Aviv—and

00:03:23.959 --> 00:03:25.750
yesterday, what the Lord showed us

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:28.229
about Taiwan.

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:32.509
We're praying into the future.

00:03:32.519 --> 00:03:34.630
We don't pray into the past and the

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:36.990
present; we're praying into the future

00:03:36.990 --> 00:03:37.000
and

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:39.910
what God has for us

00:03:39.920 --> 00:03:42.550
weeks from now.

00:03:42.560 --> 00:03:44.390
So, we're not going to camp around what

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:46.390
the news is telling us. Regarding Ayatollah

00:03:46.390 --> 00:03:46.400
Khamenei,

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:49.350
I rejoice that a dictator, an

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:52.630
evil man, is no longer in power.

00:03:52.640 --> 00:03:53.430
I

00:03:53.430 --> 00:03:53.440
pray

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:55.350
he found Jesus in the last seconds of

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:56.830
his life.

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:59.390
If he didn't, he's in hell.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:02.950
We know that God had His

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:06.150
hand in this to remove evil men from

00:04:06.160 --> 00:04:07.949
torturing Christians and the underground

00:04:07.959 --> 00:04:09.430
church.

00:04:10.400 --> 00:04:12.830
Great persecution was coming on the

00:04:12.840 --> 00:04:15.550
church of Iran over the last

00:04:15.550 --> 00:04:15.560
few

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:17.069
decades,

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:19.390
and we know what the Lord showed us

00:04:19.400 --> 00:04:21.949
prior to this: the Lord

00:04:21.959 --> 00:04:25.750
said, 'I want to bring a great revival

00:04:25.760 --> 00:04:28.270
to the people of

00:04:28.270 --> 00:04:28.280
Iran.'In

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:30.670
doing so, there will be a regime

00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:33.510
change. There's going to be a shaking in

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:34.750
Iran,

00:04:34.760 --> 00:04:38.390
Pakistan,

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:41.470
Afghanistan,

00:04:41.480 --> 00:04:45.030
and all of the Arab nations.

00:04:45.040 --> 00:04:47.550
Here we are, seeing this. Why?

00:04:47.560 --> 00:04:49.590
Because the Lord said, 'Brandon,

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:51.550
you're not waiting on me to come

00:04:51.560 --> 00:04:53.590
back; I'm waiting on you. Bring in my

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.590
