00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:06.630
If you are walking with the Father,

00:05:06.640 --> 00:05:08.470
you're going to be here

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:09.670
and you're going to be there, and we're

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.830
going to be ministering to people

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:13.430
because He said there's been a

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:16.510
