00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:26.150
You're going to see one of the

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:28.230
greatest harvests of souls throughout

00:05:28.240 --> 00:05:30.350
South

00:05:30.350 --> 00:05:30.360
America—Cuba,

00:05:30.360 --> 00:05:32.270
Colombia,

00:05:32.270 --> 00:05:32.280
and

00:05:32.280 --> 00:05:35.230
Costa

00:05:36.710 --> 00:05:36.720
Rica—all

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:40.870
of

00:05:42.350 --> 00:05:42.360
it.

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:46.510
I saw a major harvest of

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:48.190
souls through Brazil. I'm telling

00:05:48.200 --> 00:05:49.750
you, ladies and gentlemen,

00:05:49.760 --> 00:05:52.750
after this is over, Cuba is next. It

00:05:52.760 --> 00:05:55.550
